Maintainer: S. Mutmainah <siti.mutmainahf@uin-suka.ac.id>
Description: Evidential contextual corrections and partial decisions using Belief Functions framework.
             This package provides functions to improve an information source such as a classifier, 
             a sensor, etc using contextual correction introduced by Pichon et al. (2016) <doi:10.1016/j.ijar.2015.12.012>. 
             Also included are tools provided to make a model using Belief Function framework and to measure the performances 
             of evidential information source using utility-discounted accuracy U65 and U80 proposed by Zaffalon et al. (2012) <doi:10.1016/j.ijar.2012.06.022>.
